Package: fuzzylink
Title: Probabilistic Record Linkage Using Pretrained Text Embeddings
Version: 0.2.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Joe", "Ornstein", , "jornstein@uga.edu", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5704-2098"))
Description: Links datasets through fuzzy string matching using pretrained text embeddings. Produces more accurate record linkage when lexical string distance metrics are a poor guide to match quality (e.g., "Patricia" is more lexically similar to "Patrick" than it is to "Trish"). Capable of performing multilingual record linkage. Methods are described in Ornstein (2025) <https://doi.org/10.1017/pan.2025.10016>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
